{"tid":860308,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《WhatsApp》騙案新手法　短訊扮「香港入境處」追數","createTime":"2018-10-13T08:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T08:59:01.000Z","uid":51464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2ff0e963e17ee11bb4ff2026ec9303a52fe866a2","tid":860308,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T08:46:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2182304\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2182304&d=FDrTDoeGdtAMKQCpECVPwvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=57629793\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2182304</a><br />\n<br />\n「入境處」電話騙案曾一度流行，騙案中騙徒會扮成入境處職員，指大陸執法部門正在找尋接聽人或其家人，其後會將電話轉駁至另 1 名扮成大陸執法部門人員的騙徒，並要求接聽人提供銀行戶口和密碼資料供調查用，再從銀行戶口中盜取金錢。隨著政府部門多次提醒市民慎防相關騙案後，大家應該已到相關詐騙電話提高警覺。不過，現在發現騙徒竟轉戰《Whatsapp》，繼續以「入境處」騙案的模式行騙！<br />\n該《Whatsapp》「入境處」騙案訊息，由「VXRL Ransomware Incident Response Center 勒索應變中心」Facebook Page 公布，該專頁指出，騙案訊息內容如下：<br />\n「依度係香港入境處<br />\n現提提你因為收到公安通知<br />\n你已經被公安通緝<br />\n請即支付 20 萬民幣解除通緝令<br />\n你可以選擇支付寶 / 銀行轉帳，支付該 20 萬人民幣」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b47ac7ff23f044faaeb18e8759669932f4a7d804","tid":860308,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T08:49:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75bf39ad15c67caafe3e74ef5b4962b78128ef80","tid":860308,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T08:51:15.000Z","msg":"都幾好做<br />\n尻send 中一個都20 萬"},{"pid":"36b44d3772d485e8729fb9fda14008871ea153e5","tid":860308,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T08:52:10.000Z","msg":"回佢：你大我呀"},{"pid":"7a356e903cdf90e726c1c3d235c41638b3794057","tid":860308,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T08:55:44.000Z","msg":"其